  • Classes in io.atlasmap.service used by io.atlasmap.service 
    Class Description
    AtlasLibraryLoader
    The class loader to achieve dynamic loading for which is required for design time backend, such as custom field action, Java Document and custom mapping.
    AtlasLibraryLoader.AtlasLibraryLoaderListener
    The interface for the event listener of the library loading/unloading event.
  • Classes in io.atlasmap.service used by io.atlasmap.standalone 
    Class Description
    AtlasService
    The AtlasMap Core Service provides basic operations which is not specific to the individual data formats, Create/Get/Update/Remove mapping definition stored in Design Time Service local storage, validate mapping, retrieve metadata for available field actions and etc.
